        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "When etched with this rune, a weapon's hilt or haft becomes engraved with grooves that match the imprints of a wolf's teeth. By putting a *fanged* weapon in your mouth, you can transform into an animal.",
